<section id="introduction" class="block-content bg-white">
	<h2>Introduction</h2>
	<p>In this task you will use template content to add a contact page with styles to the three-page 'Travel Agency' website project you <a href="../project-travel/index.html">created earlier</a>.</p>
	
	<p>You can display a <a href="https://ibat-web-dev.github.io/portfolio/travel/contact-form/index.html" target="_blank" title="Web Design Project: Travel Agency 2n2l.com Brendan Munnelly">finished version</a> of the project web pages on GitHub by clicking the image below.</p>
	<p><a href="https://ibat-web-dev.github.io/portfolio/travel/contact-form/index.html" class="img-link" target="_blank"><img SRC="assets/img/travel-finished.png" alt="Web Design Project: Travel Agency 2n2l.com Brendan Munnelly"></a></p>

